            <title><![CDATA[【[感冒]#甲流和乙流会交叉感染吗#】医生介绍，流感病毒可分为甲、乙、丙三型，其中，甲流和乙流都可能出现发烧、肌肉酸痛等症状。[话筒]医生提醒：①得过甲流或...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[感冒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ganmao-286fc59b6d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E5%92%8C%E4%B9%99%E6%B5%81%E4%BC%9A%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B2%E6%B5%81%E5%92%8C%E4%B9%99%E6%B5%81%E4%BC%9A%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%89%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#甲流和乙流会交叉感染吗#</span></a>】医生介绍，流感病毒可分为甲、乙、丙三型，其中，甲流和乙流都可能出现发烧、肌肉酸痛等症状。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒：①得过甲流或乙流中的一种，短期内仍可能感染上另一种；②做好个人防护，建议接种流感疫苗，经常开窗通风；③青霉素、头孢等对乙流无效，不建议一发烧就擅自使用抗生素。（江苏新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4986526497439806" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">江苏新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/001q6ELGly8hlhrrq7owuj60go0ag0to02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/xcq70KRflx08btS0isww01041201vbVo0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704964621&amp;ssig=PNjc0UyOio&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/4976SB94lx08btRZllzG01041200IVqN0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704964621&amp;ssig=EvFOAiMo1M&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/9objEmnClx08btRZCQYU01041200r5gq0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704964621&amp;ssig=UgolPgF2va&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4986526497439806" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
